HOW TO USE DATABASE API

examples down below.

infpr04.esy.es/recipe.php
infpr04.esy.es/recipe.php?id=5

infpr04.esy.es/login.php?user=user&pass=pass

infpr04.esy.es/register.php?user=bob&pass=water

infpr04.esy.es/search.php?input=pizza
infpr04.esy.es/search.php?input=chicken&category=pizza
infpr04.esy.es/search.php?input=&category=pizza                 //<-- category search only

infpr04.esy.es/bookmark.php?user=user&add=5    //adds recept index 5
infpr04.esy.es/bookmark.php?user=user&remove=5    //removes recept index 5
infpr04.esy.es/bookmark.php?user=admin    //get data of specific user

infpr04.esy.es/rate.php?user=user&add=20&val=10 //adds rating to recipe number 20 (ratings between 0 and 10)
infpr04.esy.es/rate.php?user=user&remove=20 	//removes rating of recipe number 20
infpr04.esy.es/rate.php?user=user 		//returns ratings of specific user